  "texts": [
    "We categorize evaluation indicators into two categories: quality indicators and indicators of the environmental complexity.",
    "Quality indicators measure the performance or effectiveness of an algorithm to assess how well an algorithm accomplishes its goal.",
    "On the other hand, Indicators of the environment's complexity provide the context regarding the difficulty and constraints of which the agents face in their environments to achieve their goal.",
    "In the following subsections, we propose several unified indicators.",
    "In Sect. 2.3.1, we discuss quality indicators."
